Developer Terms of Use
des:
Fitness Coach is a skill to help you finish short workouts at home with no equipment.

You can say:

"Alexa, open Fitness Coach"
"Alexa, start Fitness Coach"
"Alexa, launch Fitness Coach"

Once started, say "Yes" to start the workout, "Help" to get detailed instructions or "No" to quit the skill. You can also say "Stop" to exist the skill.

Exercises that may come up in the skill include:
- Squats
- Push Ups
- Sit Ups
- Burpees
- Lunges
- Jumping jacks
- High knees 
- Plank
- Mountain climber
- Tuck jumps
- Wall sits
- Lying leg raises
- Plus more to come!!

If you love this skill, please review! 

You can also send any feedback regarding the skill to echoro.voice@gmail.com and we will consider your recommendations. Your feedback helps us to create amazing new Alexa skills, thanks!
